title: f4rmacist
author: f4rmacist
content: Have you guys ever heard about Hooker Cash? They did a relaunch and with the FPS game coming on mobile and steam, might not be a bad play. A little on the pay to win side but the ingame buys will reflect on the charts.

comments.author: Xal0lex
comments.body: One of the many and unknown tokens on the BSC. Every day dozens of such projects appear on this network. Judging by the address of this smart contract, https://bscscan.com/token/0x391b12Cba7e5848FA1240550D972E477d4cAcaE3?a=0x3be1aca32328d7f3ed97db8f9e36fded4ec055e6, the project is not in any demand, has 6 holders, and 99% of all token issue is concentrated in the address of token owner. The project is more dead than alive. For a year, since the creation of the smart contract, absolutely no development.
